程序包 com.group_91.customer.entities

类 SuitInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.group_91.customer.entities.SuitInfo
  • public class SuitInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines a suit object. It is NOT the suit customer ordered, but a particular information of a suit. After instantiated, static variables can be accessed all the time.
